{"lemma":"دَفَّيْ","slug":"دَفَّيْ","root":"د.ف.ف","root_slug":"د-ف-ف","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ف-ف","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12685","n12690","n12775"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to flap the wings (of a bird)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"side, lateral surface"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"tambourine"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"A more primitive form of دَفَعَ (dafaʕa, “to push, to propel”), and its resultant noun, already formed before Arabic, though Aramaic דפא / ܕܦܐ (dappā, “board”) is believed to derive from Sumerian 𒁳 (DAB, “board”) / 𒁾 (DUB, “board”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12685","headword_ar":"دَفِيَ","root":"dfA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA^N","text_ar":"دَفَاٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, * TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZamaA^N","text_ar":"ظَمَاٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zamiy^a","text_ar":"ظَمِيَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA='apN","text_ar":"دَفَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"karaAhapN","text_ar":"كَرَاهَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kariha","text_ar":"كَرِهَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) said of a man, (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M,* K: *) [generally meaning the former: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"difo'N","text_ar":"دِفْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below:] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he experienced"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warmth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 295:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wore what rendered him warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiy^a mina","text_ar":"دَفِيَ مِنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Albarodi","text_ar":"البَرْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he wore warm clothing to protect himself from the cold"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Mgh:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tdf~A^","text_ar":"تدفّا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlv~awobi","text_ar":"بِالثَّوْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstdfA^","text_ar":"استدفا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlvwb","text_ar":"بالثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aid~afaA^a","text_ar":"اِدَّفَاَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bAlvwb","text_ar":"بالثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":", the last of these verbs [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AidotafaA^a","text_ar":"اِدْتَفَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifotaEala","text_ar":"اِفْتَعَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He warmed himself with the garment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] are said of him who has clad himself with that which renders him warm, or hot: (S:) or the meaning [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstdfA^ bAlvwb","text_ar":"استدفا بالثوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he desired warmth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heat, by means of the garment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aid~afayotu","text_ar":"اِدَّفَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotadofayotu","text_ar":"اِسْتَدْفَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occur, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ad~fA^t","text_ar":"ادّفات"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstdfA^t","text_ar":"استدفات"},{"kind":"text","text":", as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I wore what rendered me warm, or hot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T, TA.*) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiy^a Albayotu","text_ar":"دَفِيَ البَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The tent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chamber, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafuw^a","text_ar":"دَفُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA='apN","text_ar":"دَفَا=ءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a tent, or house, or chamber, ISk, T, and a day, Msb, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, T, M, Msb, K, TA.) [And"},{"kind":"page_break","n":889},{"kind":"text","text":"in like manner, a garment; as is implied in the S.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafuw^ato layolatunaA","text_ar":"دَفُوَتْ لَيْلَتُنَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our night was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA^a","text_ar":"دَفَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA","text_ar":"دَفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dfw","text_ar":"دفو"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","Mgh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n12690","headword_ar":"دَفِيٌ","root":"dfA^","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Warmly clad;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) applied to a man; (S, TA;) fem. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoA=nu","text_ar":"دَفْا=نُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoA^aY","text_ar":"دَفْاَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, M, Msb, K;) and pl., of the masc. and fem.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"difaA='N","text_ar":"دِفَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiYo'N","text_ar":"دَفِىْءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to IAar, who cites, as an ex., the following verse:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"yabiytu A^abuw layolaY dafiyoy^FA waDayofuhu\n                      \n                     \n                        mina Alqur~i yuDoHiY musotaHiq~FA xaSaAy^ilaho"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Aboo-Leylà passes the night warmly clad, while his guest, by reason of the cold, becomes deserving of his properties"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, TA:) though it has been asserted that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoA=nu","text_ar":"دَفْا=نُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and its fem. are applied peculiarly to human beings; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiYo'N","text_ar":"دَفِىْءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", peculiarly to time and place; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiy^o'N","text_ar":"دَفِيْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to a human being and to time and place: (TA:) [for] this last signifies [also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) [and so does each of the two other epithets:] you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayotN dafiy^N","text_ar":"بَيْتٌ دَفِيٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiYo'N","text_ar":"دَفِىْءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, O, TA, [though this is said in the Msb to be not allowable,]) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot, tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"house"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chamber,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and in like manner ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawobN dafiYo'N","text_ar":"ثَوْبٌ دَفِىْءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a warm garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, M, O, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yawomN dafiYo'N","text_ar":"يَوْمٌ دَفِىْءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, O, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoA=nN","text_ar":"دَفْا=نٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA from Expositions of the Fs) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot, day"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN adfiyoy^apN","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ َدفِيْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, O, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafoA^aY","text_ar":"دَفْاَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA from the Expositions of the Fs) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot, night"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN dafiy^apN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ دَفِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafiyoy^apN","text_ar":"دَفِيْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"madofaA^apN","text_ar":"مَدْفَاَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a warm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hot, land;"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. of the last"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"madaAfiy^u","text_ar":"مَدَافِيُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","M","Msb","S","O","T","K"]},{"entry_id":"n12775","headword_ar":"دَفِىَ","root":"dfw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadofaY","text_ar":"يَدْفَى"},{"kind":"text","text":",] inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafFA","text_ar":"دَفًا"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adofaY","text_ar":"اَدْفَى"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in any of the senses of this epithet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) [See also 4.]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafawotu AljariyHa","text_ar":"دَفَوْتُ الجَرِيحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, TA, [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafayotu","text_ar":"دَفَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adofuwhu","text_ar":"اَدْفُوهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafowN","text_ar":"دَفْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAfayotuhu","text_ar":"دَافَيْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adofayotuhu","text_ar":"اَدْفَيْتُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A'Obeyd, S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I despatched the wounded man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastened and completed his slaughter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made his slaughter sure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"certain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, S, K:) and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAfaA^otuhu","text_ar":"دَافَاْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adofaA^otuhu","text_ar":"اَدْفَاْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAfaqotuhu","text_ar":"دَافَقْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: see 3 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"df","text_ar":"دف"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. Accord. to Ibn-Abi-l-Hadeed,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaY","text_ar":"دَفَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA","text_ar":"دَفَا"},{"kind":"text","text":",] sometimes pronounced with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dafaA^a","text_ar":"دَفَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slew,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the dial. of Kináneh. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA"]}]}}